2026-02-21 13:11:30,887 - conversation - INFO - Conversation: Tom Moreno: Here's what I'd do — we need a mix of ambient and task lighting. Battery-powered spotlights for visual interest, but with wired backup in case of wind. Should hold up fine under Isabella's dancing routine.
