2026-02-21 13:13:10,904 - conversation - INFO - Conversation: Mrs. Peterson: Oh, that reminds me of a student I had in 1987 — little Timmy Williams. He brought his dad's old tools to show off at our Valentine's party every year, and I always encouraged him to share his passion. Now, dear, that has real potential for community bonding! You know what would be lovely? If we could find a way to incorporate some of the traditional elements into Isabella's party, it would create this beautiful continuity across generations.
